title: Maplestory Marketplace
description: A fair and ethical marketplace system for the video game Maplestory, addressing issues like unfair trades and market manipulation. Leveraging historical data and market trends, the system suggests fair prices, promotes transparent trading, and includes a reputation system for reliable service exchange.

title: Dressing Up My Virtual Friends: An ACNH Clothing Recommender
description: A clothing recommendation system for Animal Crossing: New Horizons (ACNH) to help players gift items matching each villager's style preferences. Using datasets detailing villager attributes and clothing items, the system suggests outfits to enhance in-game friendships.

title: Detecting Anomalies in Solar Power Generation
description: Anomaly detection system for solar power generation using a time-series dataset with over 2.6 billion rows from 20,000 solar PV systems in the UK. Utilizing PySpark, this project identifies outliers in power generation, aiding companies in maintaining efficient and sustainable energy output.

title: Discord Bot
description: Discord bot using JavaScript, including functionalities such as polls, calendars, scheduling, reminders, and image generation to facilitate classmate activities.
